title: Catch & Cook Invasive Crawfish Boil - Catching Muddy Red Swamp Crawdads and Cooking Them For Dinner.

media:group.media:title: Catch & Cook Invasive Crawfish Boil - Catching Muddy Red Swamp Crawdads and Cooking Them For Dinner.
media:group.media:description: In this video we do some hunting/gathering for wild food by catching invasive swamp crayfish and cooking them in a crawfish boil. My kids loved catching them but thought the boil was spicy.
